hefly.com/?p=69\";s:11:\"description\";s:1127:\"<h3><a href=\"http://thethefly.com/2475/theme/thethe-photographer/\" target=\"_blank\">TheThe Photographer Theme Released</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://thethefly.com/2475/theme/thethe-photographer/\" target=\"_blank\"><img align=\"right\" style=\"margin-left:10px;\" src=\"http://news.thethefly.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/screenshot2.png\" alt=\"TheThe Photographer\" title=\"TheThe Photographer\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-70\" /></a></p>\n<p>We have created a photoblogging theme that is customizable enough and high-end enough for a professional photographer, but also managed to make it so easy to use that anyone with a camera could implement it for his/her personal photoblog.</p>\n<p>TheThe Photographer, our newest offering, is the offspring of months of hard work and applied experience on the part of Vladimir Verbetskiy, Alex Kkalyuzhnyi, Pavel Tsydik, and Yuriy Sorochev. The sliders slide, the arrows point, and the drop-down menus drop with just a little bit more zest than before.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://thethefly.com/2475/theme/thethe-photographer/\" target=\"_blank\">Read more &gt;&gt;</a> </p>\n\";s:7:\"content\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";s:1127:\"<h3><a href=\"http://thethefly.com/2475/theme/thethe-photographer/\" target=\"_blank\">TheThe Photographer Theme Released</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://thethefly.com/2475/theme/thethe-photographer/\" target=\"_blank\"><img align=\"right\" style=\"margin-left:10px;\" src=\"http://news.thethefly.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/screenshot2.png\" alt=\"TheThe Photographer\" title=\"TheThe Photographer\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-70\" /></a></p>\n<p>We have created a photoblogging theme that is customizable enough and high-end enough for a professional photographer, but also managed to make it so easy to use that anyone with a camera could implement it for his/her personal photoblog.</p>\n<p>TheThe Photographer, our newest offering, is the offspring of months of hard work and applied experience on the part of Vladimir Verbetskiy, Alex Kkalyuzhnyi, Pavel Tsydik, and Yuriy Sorochev. The sliders slide, the arrows point, and the drop-down menus drop with just a little bit more zest than before.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://thethefly.com/2475/theme/thethe-photographer/\" target=\"_blank\">Read more &gt;&gt;</a> </p>\n\";}s:3:\"wfw\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentrss\";s:74:\"http://news.thethefly.com/2011/09/thethe-photographer-theme-released/feed/\";}s:5:\"slash\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";s:1:\"0\";}s:7:\"summary\";s:1127:\"<h3><a href=\"http://thethefly.com/2475/theme/thethe-photographer/\" target=\"_blank\">TheThe Photographer Theme Released</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://thethefly.com/2475/theme/thethe-photographer/\" target=\"_blank\"><img align=\"right\" style=\"margin-left:10px;\" src=\"http://news.thethefly.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/screenshot2.png\" alt=\"TheThe Photographer\" title=\"TheThe Photographer\" width=\"300\" height=\"225\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-70\" /></a></p>\n<p>We have created a photoblogging theme that is customizable enough and high-end enough for a professional photographer, but also managed to make it so easy to use that anyone with a camera could implement it for his/her personal photoblog.</p>\n<p>TheThe Photographer, our newest offering, is the offspring of months of hard work and applied experience on the part of Vladimir Verbetskiy, Alex Kkalyuzhnyi, Pavel Tsydik, and Yuriy Sorochev. The sliders slide, the arrows point, and the drop-down menus drop with just a little bit more zest than before.</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://thethefly.com/2475/theme/thethe-photographer/\" target=\"_blank\">Read more &gt;&gt;</a> </p>\n\";s:12:\"atom_content\";s:1127:\"<h3><a href=\"http://thethefly.com/2475/theme/thethe-photographer/\" target=\"_blank\">TheThe Photographer Theme Released</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"http://thethefly.com/2475/theme/thethe-photogr