   <div id=\"feeshighlight\">\n            <p align=\"justify\"><b>*One-Time Fee of S$203</b> <b><strong>(non-refundable) </strong></b>for Pre-Course Activities and Matriculation <font color=red>(NSMen are only required to pay in the year of admission)</font>. </p>\n            <p align=\"justify\" > \n      **The online credit card payment of confirmation fee can be made via <a href=\"https://eservices.smu.edu.sg/psp/ps/?cmd=login\" target=\"_blank\">Applicant\'s Self Service</a>.</p>\n<p align=\"justify\" >You may check the payment status via <a href=\"https://eservices.smu.edu.sg/psp/ps/?cmd=login\" target=\"_blank\">Applicant\'s Self Service</a> (Student Admission or Online Matriculation &gt; View Payment Status).\n            </p>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    [/accordion]\n    [accordion title=\"Step 2 - Update/Verify of Personal Data\"]\n	         <div>Login to <a href=\"https://eservices.smu.edu.sg/psp/ps/?cmd=login\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Applicant\'s Self Service</strong></a>  (https://eservices.smu.edu.sg/psp/ps/?cmd=login)<br>\n<strong>Navigation Path: Self Service&gt; Online Matriculation&gt; Confirm Personal Data </strong><br>\n<br>\n<p> Please take some time to confirm/update your personal data as captured in the official records. It is important for the University to maintain accurate data in case of emergencies. </p>\n</div>\n[/accordion]\n[accordion title=\"Step 3 Part 1: Matriculate Online\"]\n      <div>Login to <a href=\"https://eservices.smu.edu.sg/psp/ps/?cmd=login\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Applicant\'s Self Service</strong></a>  (https://eservices.smu.edu.sg/psp/ps/?cmd=login)<br>\n        <strong>Navigation Path: Self Service&gt; Online Matriculation &gt; Matriculate Online</strong><br>\n        <br>        \n        <p>Please ensure that you have completed Step 1 and Step 2, at least 2 working days before you proceed with this step. Kindly ensure that all matriculation information is accurate.</p>\n        <p align=\"center\"><strong>Important Note</strong>: For students <span class=\"red\">below 18 years old</span>, please print out the indemnity form for submission during <strong>Part 2: IDs Verification Day</strong>.</p>\n        <table width=\"500px\"  border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n          <tr>\n            <td width=\"500\" bgcolor=\"#CCFFFF\" ><div class=\"ctrtext\"><strong>Part 1 - ONLINE MATRICULATION<br>\n                <br> \n                Date: 18 June 2012, 9.00am - 16 July 2012, 5.00pm</strong>\n                \n                <br>\n                <br>\n                (Note: Pay a non-refundable Confirmation Fee* by <span class=\"red\">12 July 2012</span>. Please wait for 2 working days for payment to be updated in the system.) <br>\n                </div></td>\n          </tr>\n        </table>\n        <p>&nbsp;</p>\n      </div>\n [/accordion]\n [accordion title=\"Step 4 - Activate SMU Computer Account\"]\n\n      <div>\n        <p>Login to <a href=\"https://eservices.smu.edu.sg/psp/ps/?cmd=login\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Applicant\'s Self Service</strong></a> (https://eservices.smu.edu.sg/psp/ps/?cmd=login)<br>\n<strong> Navigation Path: Self Service&gt; Online Matriculation &gt; Activate SMU Computer Account</strong> </p>\n<p>Please remember your new SMU user ID &amp; Password. You will require your SMU computer account to access SMU\'s network resources such as\n\n\nthe student portal OASIS as well as the campus email.</p>\n        <p>Henceforth, you must use your SMU Email Account to correspond with SMU. Important email will be sent to that email account. Please check it regularly. </p>\n      </div>\n      [/accordion]\n\n    \n       	\n	        [accordion title=\"Step 5 - Upload Photograph\"]\n	\n	      <div>\n	       <p>Login to <a href=\"https://oasis.smu.edu.sg\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Student Portal OASIS</strong></a> (https://oasis.smu.edu.sg)<br>\n          <strong>Navigation Path: OASIS> Home> Pre-Term Activities and Info> Upload Student Photograph</strong></p>\n        <p>Please use the newly activated account and login to the student portal  <a href=\"https://oasis.smu.edu.sg\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> OASIS</strong></a> (https://oasis.smu.edu.sg).\n      \n          <a href=\"http://info.smu.edu.sg/courses/Part_1_Matriculation/SMU_Guidelines_on_Taking_Photograph.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">          Approved photographs</a> will be used for printing onto the SMU Student Card, which will be issued to you during the IDs Verification Day. Applicants who have uploaded their photograph earlier will not need to re-submit, unless the photograph uploaded earlier does not meet SMU’s specification and is rejected. </p>\n        <p><span class=\"ctrtext\"><span class=\"style2\">Note:</span> Student\'s photograph must be submitted online by <u>16 July 2012, 5.00pm</u>.</span></p>\n \n	      </div>\n	      [/accordion]\n    \n\n       \n [accordion title=\"Step 6 - Update Bank Information\"]\n	\n	      <div>\n	       <p>Login to <a href=\"https://oasis.smu.edu.sg\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Student Portal OASIS</strong></a> (https://oasis.smu.edu.sg)<br>\n          <strong>Navigation Path: OASIS> Home> Pre-Term Activities and Info> Upload Student Photograph</strong></p>\n        <p>Please use the newly activated account and login to the student portal  <a href=\"https://oasis.smu.edu.sg\" target=\"_blank\"><strong> OASIS</strong></a> (https://oasis.smu.edu.sg).\n      \n          <a href=\"http://info.smu.edu.sg/courses/Part_1_Matriculation/SMU_Guidelines_on_Taking_Photograph.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">          Approved photographs</a> will be used for printing onto the SMU Student Card, which will be issued to you during the IDs Verification Day. Applicants who have uploaded their photograph earlier will not need to re-submit, unless the photograph uploaded earlier does not meet SMU’s specification and is rejected. </p>\n        <p><span class=\"ctrtext\"><span class=\"style2\">Note:</span> Student\'