ule below.\r\nNOTE:\r\n\r\n- This matriculation exercise is only applicable to students who are commencing their studies in August 2011.\r\n\r\n- Applicants who have just accepted the offer would need to allow 3 working days before proceeding to perform online matriculation.\r\n\r\n<strong>Step1 Make Payment(at least 2 days prior to step 3) </strong>\r\nLogin to Applicant\'s Self Service (https://eservices.smu.edu.sg/psp/ps/?cmd=login)\r\nNavigation Path: Self Service> Online Matriculation> Make online payment \r\n\r\nMake non-refundable Confirmation fee* of $203 via credit card** or AXS Payment Stations available island-wide.\r\nNote: Allow 2 working days for payment to be updated in the system. Please make payment latest by 30 July 2011.\r\n*One-Time Fee of S$203 (non-refundable) for Pre-Course Activities and Matriculation (NSMen are only required to pay in the year of admission).\r\n**The online credit card payment of confirmation fee can be made via Applicant\'s Self Service.\r\nYou may check the payment status via Applicant\'s Self Service (Student Admission or Online Matriculation > View Payment Status).','Singaporean','','inherit','open','open','','84-revision-3','','','2012-04-23 09:16:35','2012-04-23 09:16:35','',84,'http://matt2012.super.21marinabay.com/84-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),(171,1,'2012-04-30 04:53:12','2012-04-30 04:53:12','\r\n\r\n[accordions title=\"Accordion Group Title\" active=1 event=\"click\" autoheight=true]\r\n[accordion title=\"Step 1 - Make Payment (at least 2 days prior to Step 3)\"]\r\n<div>Login to <a href=\"https://eservices.smu.edu.sg/psp/ps/?cmd=login\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Applicant\'s Self Service</strong></a> (https://eservices.smu.edu.sg/psp/ps/?cmd=login)<br>\r\n        <strong>Navigation Path: Self Service&gt; Online Matriculation&gt; Make online payment <br>\r\n        <br>\r\n        </strong>        \r\n        <p>Make non-refundable Confirmation fee* of <strong>$203</strong> via credit card** or <a href=\"downloads/AXS%20Payment%20Guide.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">AXS Payment Stations </a>available island-wide. </p>\r\n        <p><span class=\"red\"><strong>Note</strong></span>: Allow 2 working days for payment to be updated in the system. Please make payment latest by<span class=\"red\"> 12 July 2012</span>. </p>\r\n        <div id=\"feeshighlight\">\r\n            <p align=\"justify\"><b>*One-Time Fee of S$203</b> <b><strong>(non-refundable) </strong></b>for Pre-Course Activities and Matriculation <font color=red>(NSMen are only required to pay in the year of admission)</font>. </p>\r\n            <p align=\"justify\" > \r\n      **The online credit card payment of confirmation fee can be made via <a href=\"https://eservices.smu.edu.sg/psp/ps/?cmd=login\" target=\"_blank\">Applicant\'s Self Service</a>.</p>\r\n<p align=\"justify\" >You may check the payment status via <a href=\"https://eservices.smu.edu.sg/psp/ps/?cmd=login\" target=\"_blank\">Applicant\'s Self Service</a> (Student Admission or Online Matriculation &gt; View Payment Status).\r\n            </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n      </div>\r\n    [/accordion]\r\n    [accordion title=\"Step 2 - Update/Verify of Personal Data\"]\r\n	         <div>Login to <a href=\"https://eservices.smu.edu.sg/psp/ps/?cmd=login\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Applicant\'s Self Service</strong></a>  (https://eservices.smu.edu.sg/psp/ps/?cmd=login)<br>\r\n<strong>Navigation Path: Self Service&gt; Online Matriculation&gt; Confirm Personal Data </strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<p> Please take some time to confirm/update your personal data as captured in the official records. It is important for the University to maintain accurate data in case of emergencies. </p>\r\n</div>\r\n[/accordion]\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n[accordion title=\"Step 3 Part 1: Matriculate Online\"]\r\n      <div>Login to <a href=\"https://eservices.smu.edu.sg/psp/ps/?cmd=login\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>Applicant\'s Self Service</strong></a>  (https://eservices.smu.edu.sg/psp/ps/